    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Want to step up your cooking, baking and meal prep game? Then you need the Beille nylon kitchen ladle in stylish wood and charcoal grey finish. These ladles are made with high heat resistant nylon that will stand up to all the wear and tear your kitchen dishes out, whether pairing the ladle with a punch bowl, serving out pasta sauce or a new batch of homemade soup. The ladle or serveware spoon features a solid nylon head, is dishwasher safe and can be used with both hot and cold food ingredients. Our ladle has a sturdy handle made of durable wood, so you can count on it to last, while the ergonomic handle design with upper soft grip will provide comfort and help prevent slippage when cooking or serving</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Beille Grey Kitchen Utensils Set High Heat Resistance Spoon Ladle (Many Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Want to step up your cooking and meal prep game? Then you need Beille kitchen utensil tools! These spoons, spatulas, and ladles are made with food-grade materials that does not cause harmful chemical contamination of food like other similar utensils.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>ESSENTIAL KITCHEN UTENSILS - Beille utensils are a must-have kitchen tool for cooking, meal, and food prep. Large wooden handle with a broad spatula base will quickly and safely turn food while cooking and keep your hands safe from heat</li>\n    <li>FOOD GRADE MATERIALS - Kitchen spatula made of food-grade materials which do not cause harmful chemical contamination of food like other similar spatulas. Silicone and Wheat Straw are certified BPA-free and food-safe</li>\n    <li>SOLID AND DURABLE - Beille utensils use materials that mimic traditional plastic spatulas and food turners without harmful byproducts. Solid-head spatula is dishwasher safe and can be used with both hot and cold food ingredients</li>\n    <li>ERGONOMIC HANDLE - Sturdy handle made of durable materials so you can count on it to last, and ergonomic handle provides comfort during use; Comes with handy slot in handle for easy hang storage if preferred; Trendy color will fit nicely with any kitchen decor</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Colors: grey, wood; Material: nylon, wood; Dimensions: 11.5 x 3.2 inches</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/home/kitchen/YJJ-75499-72_ladel_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"Want to step up your cooking and meal prep game\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> BLECKTLS</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Gray</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 13 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The silicone or wheat straw tools mimic traditional plastic utensils and food turners without harmful byproducts. It features a solid head, is dishwasher safe, and can be used with hot and cold food ingredients.</p>\n  <p>Our tools a sturdy handle made of durable material so you can count on it to last, and the ergonomic handle design will provide comfort and help prevent slippage during use. The handle features a handy slot for easy hang storage if preferred, and it comes in a sleek, trendy color that will fit nicely with just about any kitchen decor.</p>\n  <p>Every kitchen needs a reliable, durable, and solid spatula. With the Beille kitchen utensils, you can cook and meal prep with peace of mind knowing you’re doing your part to protect yourself, your family, and the planet from harmful plastics.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Want to step up your cooking, baking and meal prep game? Then you need the Beille nylon kitchen ladle in stylish wood and charcoal grey finish. These ladles are made with high heat resistant nylon that will stand up to all the wear and tear your kitchen dishes out, whether pairing the ladle with a punch bowl, serving out pasta sauce or a new batch of homemade soup. The ladle or serveware spoon features a solid nylon head, is dishwasher safe and can be used with both hot and cold food ingredients. Our ladle has a sturdy handle made of durable wood, so you can count on it to last, while the ergonomic handle design with upper soft grip will provide comfort and help prevent slippage when cooking or serving.",
